Ehh, got this for my wife, it was long, boring, and didn't really cover what she was looking for. I'm sure there are better ones out there.
My makeup became much better with this DVD . I use nude look every day, and I constantly get complements from my husband.

This is one of the stupidist made video's I have ever seen. It could have been a very good dvd, with many of good tips and advise, and actually showing the makeup techniques close up so you could really tell what the makeup artist was doing. However who ever produced it, truly ruined it by making it so hard to move on to another model after you saw the first look the artist done up. It is in various languages and it does not automatically move so you can get the next model. It either puts you on another model in another language or it keeps repeating the same model in English. To get to another model being made up you have to mess so much it actually is disgusting and you can spend 5 to 10 minutes trying to find a new one so by the time you get to one you don't even want to watch it. I would love to be able to tell who's bright Idea it was to set the video up like they did that they ruined what could have been a very good video, (full of great advise and with a very good makeupu artist) well a least the 3 of the 14 models I watched was, before getting so disgusted with trying to get to a new model, that I just gave up and have not seen the other 11 models makeover.
purchased to give more education to my students (cosmetology). it is a great tool to use, my students learned a great deal from the dvd. great condition, shipping was fast,

I got this for my lady ... personally I kind of like a little make-up on her ... but she did not really get it right a lot of times.  Now she does the nude look and other tricks  ... anyway, looks good on her.
I recommend it .... from my second hand point of view.
